quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  26,184,"And be fearful of the One who created you and the former generations.""
  26,185,"They said, "You are but one of the bewitched men."
  26,186,"And you are no more than a human like us, and in fact we consider you to be one of the liars."
  26,187,"So cause a piece from the sky to fall down upon us, if you are one of the truthful.""
  26,188,"He said, 'My Lord knows best what you do.""
  26,189,"Thus they belied him, so they were seized by the torment of the Day of Canopy. Indeed it was the punishment of a terrible day."
  26,190,"Surely in this there is a sign, but most of them are not to believe."
  26,191,"Add surely your Lord is the Mighty, the Merciful."
  26,192,"And this (Qur'an) is the revelation of the Lord of the worlds."
  26,193,"It is brought by the Trusted Spirit down"
  26,194,"to your heart, so that you become one of the warners"
  26,195,"in plain Arabic language."
  26,196,"And of course, it is (mentioned) in the scriptures of the former people."
  26,197,"Is it not a proof for them that the knowledgeable of the children of Isra'il recognize him (the prophet)?"
  26,198,"And (even) if We had revealed it to a non-Arab,"
  26,199,"and he would have recited it to them, they were not to believe in it."
  26,200,"Thus We have made it enter into the hearts of the sinners."
  26,201,"They will not believe in it until they will see the painful punishment"
  26,202,"and it will come to them suddenly while they will not be anticipating (it),"
  26,203,"and they will say, "Is it (possible) that we are given some respite?""
  26,204,"Are they asking then that Our punishment should come soon?"
  26,205,"So tell me, If We give them enjoyment for years,"
  26,206,"then comes to them what they are warned of,"